channel.title: Why my internet is going so slow?
channel.description:
So... 2 days ago my internet was fine, and over night.. It became slow?.. This happened on only my computer, my brothers computer is still fast, so is my moms and my dads too..
So does anybody know a reason for this?
On the upside.. My upload speed tripled..
Normally it would give me this on a speed test.. [IMG]http://www.speedtest.net/result/137181044.png[/img]
Now its gives this.. [IMG]http://www.speedtest.net/result/153708892.png[/img]

Comcast sucks i have it to. One thing i do because the same happens to me is you delete all the history,cookies, and all that junk.
Also go to local disk C then right click,go to properties and click disck cleanup up put only clean recycle bin,and a few others. Here are the ones not to clean i repeat DONT clean these log files, office set up, Dont compress old files. Ur internet should work better then.
